{"tid":2424924,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"心態或者方法唔變，好難喺股票度賺錢","createTime":"2021-02-27T04:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T08:21:15.000Z","uid":181257,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c79c983a4928c985757d32e579ab343306221fc4","tid":2424924,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"越多人買，越危險。開始多人講，多人留意嘅時候，就係走鬼嘅時候，連登就成日出現咁嘅情況。無論玩咩都係，賭百家樂係咁，買股票都係咁。如果阿豬阿狗買都贏，呢個世界無窮人。千奇唔好人講就去買，輸撚死<br />\n<br />\n另外， 諗嘢要諗遠啲，要有前瞻性。當你諗到/留意到 其他人將會有興趣嘅東西，你就發達。例如之前炒嘅無人駕駛概念，星際移民等等。未來會係DNA技術，新藥物同AI 醫療<br />\n<br />\n跌市時不妨留意吓邊啲股票係有錢入，個價之前無乜點升，而家又無乜點跌，或者跌少少，嗰啲就可以買得過<br />\n<br />\n跌市通常只係大户嚇鳩你等你散貨佢再入平嘢，等個市升，佢出貨，你又接番火棒，不斷loop。乜嘢債息上到1.6，驚通脹導致跌市呢啲原因，真係聽到都覺得on撚鳩。"},{"pid":"cc1369eb3350bd4381e4bdacc15fdd211879c1e7","tid":2424924,"uid":49648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9034c4fd2436e072801ede537d15597cbc4b63a","tid":2424924,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"你好似幾有料，可唔可以收我做徒弟？"},{"pid":"22a7746e99a1ab67372ed5c1ddeb30d6bc88aff9","tid":2424924,"uid":181257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9034c4fd2436e072801ede537d15597cbc4b63a","tid":2424924,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"你好似幾有料，可唔可以收我做徒弟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"我都係睇你啲po學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ac36c4e99520325ba17c1cd45410dc7108d0b0","tid":2424924,"uid":84926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"如果人人都心想事成<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n唔通真係人人鳩買都贏錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6981b8241ae575cc44219d716abb29df22e4f587","tid":2424924,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"係，最近開始入左AAL  ， 打算坐返幾個月， 原本打算入科技股，個個都話升緊，但個價太高。。驚一跌就好金，唔敢入<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸: 新手"},{"pid":"898097bc04db8987fd66e9c33556e171872d6fa5","tid":2424924,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"算吧啦<br />\n<br />\n贏錢只有少數人<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔輸錢 個市會好難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b128fb1f435361dee831ca86f85c585dee7aa7","tid":2424924,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ac36c4e99520325ba17c1cd45410dc7108d0b0","tid":2424924,"uid":84926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"如果人人都心想事成<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n唔通真係人人鳩買都贏錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"輸得多都要諗方法改進架 <br />\n一係就完全唔玩，繼續玩就要諗方法過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329d53dd318049edc498b3fba7151dbc4318c739","tid":2424924,"uid":21872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6dPxkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6dPxkY.jpg&h=59540a5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b8ffb4fab6263475c3497b3e37fb36a74bfd557","tid":2424924,"uid":262035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"啲人成日以為股市有得解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話乜債息升導致股市跌<br />\n<br />\n債息由上年8、9月就升緊無人講？<br />\n之後股市咪又係keep 住升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲所謂原因只係大戶講嚟合理化個跌市<br />\n啲傻戶又覺得好合理就人踩人咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大戶就多謝哂大家啲平貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb6ae72400d0265598f315b01d09